Objectives
1. Implement 2 additional primitives: cone and cylinder
2. Implement Constructive Solid Geometry (CSG) to allow more complex shapes to be modeled using primitives
3. Implement Texture Mapping 
4. Implement Bump Mapping
5. Implement reflective surfaces
6. Implement refractive materials
7. Implement glossy reflection/transmission
8. Implement soft shadows
9. Implement a grid-based data structure for accelerating the detection of ray-model intersections
10. Construct a final scene to be displayed.